@{b}v1.10 (01.05.96)@{ub}  -  Cleaned up code making it more adaptive for everyones use (Included Checked Disk Formatter and Dismount).

@{b}v1.02 (29.04.96)@{ub}  -  Added DMS, Rar, Zip quickly for an idea to add it to my bbs for checking of archives uploaded.



